.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, pop, soul, blues
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the fan of blues##2
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | pop   | indie | soul |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

