.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, pilot, dancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the coach is between the dancer and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| Job   | pilot  | dancer  | coach | dressmaker |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

