.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, aconite, daisy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsaconite##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Flower   | aconite | daisy       | poppy        | marigold    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

