.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, juice, soy-milk
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | juice  | water   | soy-milk      |

