The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, zinnia, aconite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, salsa, techno
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is between the fan of salsa and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
| Flower         | aconite | marigold | rose  | zinnia |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | techno      | house  | ambient     |

