.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, indian, mexican
1. the argentine is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the argentine##1
6. the nigerian is on the far right##1
7. the indian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Nationality        | mexican  | argentine      | indian        | nigerian      |

