The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
City: nizza, colone, hamburg, marseilles
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the mechanic##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to colone is between the person watching romance movies and the mechanic##2
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to colone is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | scientist | mechanic    | dancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| City     | nizza     | colone       | hamburg        | marseilles    |

