3. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | fishing   | chess           | baking         | skydiving      |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | frog | hamster | rat |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

