There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, lime, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping, board-games, drawing
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | mirinda | tea           | soy-milk |
| Food       | artichoke | lime    | kiwi          | orange   |
| Hobby      | board-games  | camping   | drawing | rock-climbing  |

