4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the pilot is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the videographer is between the person drinking milk and the electrician##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
