.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, azure, light-blue, chestnut
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color         | coral        | chestnut  | light-blue | azure   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

