.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
City: prague, new-york, hamburg, marseilles
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, skateboard
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City        | marseilles | new-york | prague | hamburg |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski | motorbike | skateboard |

 